Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear ye! Hear ye!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.11,0:00:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ponyville Foal and Filly\NFair is almost ready to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whee! Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hee hee hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because the\Nattendees are young,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean they don't deserve\Nmy very best creative work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.79,0:00:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, this puppet theatre\Nis going to be the talk
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Foal and Filly Fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How could it not be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one making it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.57,0:00:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I couldn't have\Ndone it without the help
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of one of my dearest and\Nmost supportive friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my favorite dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your favorite dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, gee.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The hours have been long, the\Nwork taxing beyond compare,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,0:00:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but it will all be\Nworth it when we hear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.96,0:01:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,those three little words--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is awful!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Awful?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely unusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't travel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no room for my puppets!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears I won't have a\Ntravelling puppet theatre
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to use after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what that\Nguy was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.20,0:01:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.77,0:01:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Subtitles by YayPonies\Nhttp://yayponies.eu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is terrible.{\i0}\N{\i1}Simply terrible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So that puppeteer didn't like\Nyour exquisitely crafted,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,best puppet theatre in the\Nhistory of puppet theatres
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,puppet theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just contribute\Nsomething else
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Foal and Filly Fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never have something\Nfinished in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to leave my\Ncreative mark on the fair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Miserably.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And that makes me miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be something\Nin here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not who, it's what.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what can help Rarity make\Nsomething in time for the fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She really, really, really wants\Nto make a creative contribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She said I'm her\Nfavourite dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's up to me to come through\Nfor her in her time of need.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be some kind of\Nspell that'll do the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hoo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, help a dragon out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who made you that\Nbow tie you liked so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think we\Nshould use magi--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo! Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo! Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo! Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If I wasn't supposed to have it,\Nit wouldn't be so easy to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's covered\Nin spikes, like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Inspiration Manifestation,\Ninstantly brings ideas to life."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm liking the\Nlooks of this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me be!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see how\Ndistraught, disappointed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and downtrodden I still am?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But I brought you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless it's another carton\Nof Vanilla Oat Swirl
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,or word that the festival\Nhas been cancelled,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'm interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, Precious Scales,\NI already have magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But not the kind that can\Nhelp you create something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in time for the fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This can!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it's worth a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,From in the head to\Nout in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Every thought to action.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold close this book,\Nand through its spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll start a chain reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Projecting forth\Nwhatever beauty you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Only when true words are spoken,\Nwill you finally be set free.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one\Nway to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about making this a\Nmuch more beautiful spell book
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, dear, Spike, here\NI was about to give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but like a true friend, you've\Ncome through with flying colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come! We must find the\Npuppeteer right away
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so that I may provide him with\Nthe most fabulous theatre
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,he's ever imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should I say that\NI've ever imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:07:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Miss Rarity, come to\Nsee the show, I presume.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll notice I had to make\Ndo in light of your recent
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,failure to produce a\Nfunctioning theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I think you'll find\Nthe new one I've created
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,will be much more\Nto your liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm yeah well, it is gorgeous,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but that was never the\Nproblem now, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well this one\Ndoes seem to travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Plenty of room for my puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, Miss Rarity, I don't\Nknow how you managed to do so
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in such a short amount of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but you seem to have\Nredeemed yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you manage to do\Nso in such a short time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact,\Nshe used a sp-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A good designer never\Nreveals her tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again, Spike, for\Nbeing such a dear friend
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and finding this book for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, guess I can return it\Nnow that the fair is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made my creative\Ncontribution as I'd hoped to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and all is well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again, perhaps I should\Nkeep it just a skotch longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mind do you, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll keep it for\Na few more hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No harm in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike! I'm so glad\Nyou're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I've never been better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This book you've\Ngiven me is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, I've been up all night\Njust creating and creating
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and creating and creating!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've completed my fall line\Nfor the next fifteen seasons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I started\Nthinking, why stop there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spike, I've always\Nthought this town of ours
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,could use a few\Nbeautifying upgrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And with this book, I can make\Nthat happen with such ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You will support me in this\Nendeavor by letting me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,keep the book just\Na little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say we get a little\Nbreakfast before we get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No time for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get\Nstarted right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically, we do have time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,because with that\Nbook held close
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you can just\Nmake things--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this is exactly\Nwhat I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why that cart hasn't an\Nounce of stylish flair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes playin'\Ntricks on me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What in rhubarb\Npie just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it gorgeous?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You should ask Applejack\Nif she wants you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to give all the Apple\Nfamily carts a makeover!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't really think I need\Nto ask permission, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone loves surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially when they're\Ngorgeous ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony does love surprises!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't even tell\Nanypony that it's me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,who is behind all the fabulous\Nchanges I'll be making.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:10:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't that be a\Nfun little secret
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,for the three of\Nus to share?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The... three of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You, me, and the\Nbook, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My marvellous,\Nmarvellous book.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me you won't\Nsay a word to anypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.81,0:11:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I could\Ncount on you, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also know just\Nwhat I want to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Get. It. Off. Of. Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always thought\NRainbow Dash
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,could use a little more glamour.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And now look at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Cloud-busting with style!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for your favorite dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ La la la la la la {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go, Mr. Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you look so content\Nin your little house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Not that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks like that's\Na door to a bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Try that one over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That leads to a...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,shoe closet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe try the staircase?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No. No. The\Nother staircase.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it gorgeous?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably the most beautiful\Nbird house ever created...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just not sure how\Nthe bird feels about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pfft. What does a bird know\Nabout architectural design?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What matters is what you\Nthink, Spike, and you love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so... "Rarity".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It is, isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.83,0:13:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But it could use a touch\Nof class, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yeah. Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This party doesn't even\Nseem to have a proper theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do something\Nabout that, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already made things\Nlook really, really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should stop\Nwhile you're ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much\Nto do elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more little\Nthing before we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, this party is certain\Nto make the society page now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't Pinkie Pie be pleased?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy happy day to--huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I am simply buzzing with ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply buzzing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But, uh, you've been at\Nthis for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Give that brilliant\Nmind of yours a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't be silly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to stop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, I won't stop until\Nevery inch of Ponyville
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,has benefited from\Nmy creative vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting with you, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:15:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything for my favorite dragon\Nand most supportive friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come! There's so\Nmuch more to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "not me, too"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, judging by that outfit, I\Nthought for sure you'd--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What? This?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to\Ntry out a new look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in that case, have you\Nseen anypony suspicious around?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.07,0:15:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The gazebo has been\Nturned into solid crystal
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and two ponies are now\Ntrapped inside its walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I made a promise to Rarity\Nto keep this to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're right\NOwlowiscious, I have to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:16:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And once I do, I can forget\NRarity thinking of me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,as her most supportive friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can forget Rarity thinking\Nof me as a friend at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised I'd keep all of\Nthis between the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's weird\Nthat she meant me, her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and the spell book, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.16,0:16:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The spell book! Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can get it away from her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet she won't be able\Nto use its magic anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.13,0:16:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, come on! It's{\i0}\N{\i1}the perfect plan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to figure\Nout which way she went.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't see!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking she's\Nheaded this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think\Nyou're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? I was just uh, basking\Nin your creative radiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spike, you do say\Nthe nicest things!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now where was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold-plated roof-tops\Nfor everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo! Hoo! Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I have just had the\Nmost marvellous idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you have;\Nyou're Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My work here in Ponyville\Nis nearly complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's time\Nthe rest of Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,benefited from my\Ncreative vision?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking we go by chariot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Or as everyone will soon\Nbe calling them, "Rariot".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! We should\Ndefinitely go by--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How...how did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, whatever do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The book. It's... I\Nmean... you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The book is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why it's right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I need my book, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done\Nwith my book?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I do anything\Nwith your book?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It was probably the owl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But, wait, I don't seem\Nto need it anymore, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel its magic\Nflowing within me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!\NI'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, the places{\i0}\N{\i1}we'll go, Spike.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Manehattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Phillydelphia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And there you'll\Nbe by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as you've always\Nbeen here in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your constant praise and\Nadoration driving me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to even greater heights
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,until there isn't an\Ninch of Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that hasn't been\Nutterly transformed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,by my creative genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, "No!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been changing things,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but you haven't been\Nmaking them better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have told you the\Ntruth at the very beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.64,0:19:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,because I was trying to be\Na supportive friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead I let you\Nbecome something awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Awful?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, you're OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I...I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Though by the looks of it,\Nsomething quite terrifying
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,has happened to Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The last part of the spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Only when true\Nwords are spoken,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,will you finally be set free."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The spell took over you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and you wanted to change\Neverything in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid to tell you\Nhow I really felt about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but then I, I told\Nyou the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dearest Spike, you should never\Nbe afraid to tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're friends, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today I learned how important it is{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to be honest with your friends{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}when they're doing something{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that you don't think is right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A true friend knows\Nthat you're speaking up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,because you care about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Never, ever, ever take another\Nbook out of the library
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,at the Castle without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadance\Nand Princess Luna
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,have much better things to do\Nthan help me clean up Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how\Nhard it was to reverse
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that much dark magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what good friends do.
